  <h1>Project Description</h1>
  <p>This project is a Blog web application created using Node.js, Express.js, and EJS. The application allows users to create and view blog posts. Posts do not persist between sessions as no database is used in this version of the application. Styling was done using bootstrap and custom css to ensure a good user experience.</p>
  <h1>Features</h1>
  <ul class="ul">
    <li>Post Creation - Users are able to create new posts.</li>
    <li>Post Viewing - The home page allows the user to view all their posts.</li>
    <li>Post Update/Delete - Users are able to edit and delete posts as needed.</li>
    <li>Styling - The application is well-styled and responsive, ensuring a good user experience on both desktop and mobile devices.</li>
  </ul>

